QuestData.Title: Fate of the Nightborne
QuestData.Description: Shortly after your victorious return from the Nighthold, urgent business took Thalyssra back to the palace.$b$bShe has requested that you meet her there.$b$bSpeak to me when you are prepared to join her.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Oculeth and meet Thalyssra in the Nighthold.

Objectives.Objective: Learn the fate of the Nightborne
